<div class='commentbox'>
RESCINDED [Warning: new strainer hazard at &quot;the Abutments,&quot; a tree completely blocking the<br/>
river-right channel at the lowest/farthest downstream old bridge pier on the Tariffville (west)<br/>
side of the river. Danger will persist at all river levels until the strainer is removed. A photo<br/>
is posted but the website is resisting an upload of a QuickTime .mov formatted video. Location:<br/>
[41.905576, -72.760363]] </div>
</td>
